ce. The University of Chicago Press. Chicago, Il.\n\nTucker, Ledyard (1958) An inter-battery method of factor analysis,\nPsychometrika, 23, 111-136.\n" [] (fetch-dataset "https://vincentarelbundock.github.io/Rdatasets/csv/psych/Thurstone.33.csv"))
